(11, '每周三奥森公园徒步，夕阳下，葱绿中，徒步走~~', '<div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-1" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">行程安排</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="mdd-zj" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: Simsun;"><span style="font-family: SimSun; font-size: 18px;">18:00 &nbsp;队员集合(奥森公园南园南门地铁B出口) 队员签到相互介绍。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: Simsun;"><span style="font-family: SimSun; font-size: 18px;">18:20 &nbsp;简单技术要点讲解及热身准备活动（最好大家一起集结，每周亲切的相聚！！）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: Simsun;"><span style="font-family: SimSun; font-size: 18px;">18:30 &nbsp;出发—— 沿5公里塑胶步道逆时针走一圈</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: Simsun;"><span style="font-family: SimSun; font-size: 18px;">19:30 &nbsp;5公里到达终点后放松整理活动，总结与合影。各回各家。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-2" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">费用说明</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">公益活动</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"></span></p></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-3" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">线路描述</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: Simsun;"><span style="font-family: SimSun; font-size: 18px;"><span style="color: rgb(96, 217, 120);"><em></em></span></span></p><span style="font-size: 16px;">你见过晚上六点的奥森吗？</span><br/><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">夕阳缓缓坠入西边的天空，</span><br/><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">夜晚来临了。</span><br/><br/><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">我们只要沿着步道、路径，</span><br/><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">走过沿路两旁的植物生长处，</span><br/><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">只要静心聆听、细心感受、循光探索，</span><br/><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">自然能发现丰富的夜间奥森。</span><br/><br/><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">每周三，我们CVA中国徒步网都会在奥森公园的南门集合</span><br/><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">欢迎你也来加入我们健康的徒步方式！！！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px